<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>旅のチケット</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;500&family=Playfair+Display:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
  <script defer src="transition.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container fade-in">
    <div class="tickets">
      <div class="ticket">
        <div class="ticket-header">
          <span>PASSENGER</span><span>BOARDING PASS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ticket-body">
          <h2>SHOMARU ✈️</h2>
          <p><strong>FROM:</strong> SECRET</p>
          <p><strong>TO:</strong> ✨ 秘密の場所 ✨</p>
          <p><strong>DATE:</strong> 2025 / 11 / 15 – 11 / 17</p>
          <p><strong>DURATION:</strong> 2泊3日</p>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="ticket-footer">
          <p>旅の始まりを、君と一緒に。</p>
          <div class="barcode"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ticket">
        <div class="ticket-header">
          <span>PASSENGER</span><span>BOARDING PASS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ticket-body">
          <h2>AYAKA ✈️</h2>
          <p><strong>FROM:</strong> SECRET</p>
          <p><strong>TO:</strong> ✨ 秘密の場所 ✨</p>
          <p><strong>DATE:</strong> 2025 / 11 / 15 – 11 / 17</p>
          <p><strong>DURATION:</strong> 2泊3日</p>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="ticket-footer">
          <p>特別な時間を、あなたと。</p>
          <div class="barcode"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="message">
      <p>少し早いけど、誕生日おめでとう。<br>
      この旅は、君への感謝とこれからの願いを込めて。<br>
      どこへ行くかは、当日までのお楽しみ。</p>
    </div>

    <body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
  color: #3b2f2f;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #f7f3ef, #efe7dc);
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

.container {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 60px 20px;
}

.title {
  font-size: 2.4rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: #5c4938;
}

.subtitle {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: #7b6a58;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.envelope {
  font-size: 4rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: transform 0.6s ease;
}

.envelope:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
}

.envelope.open {
  transform: rotateX(180deg);
}

button {
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 12px 30px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: #d2b48c;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 1rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.3s ease;
}

button:hover {
  background: #c19b6b;
}

/* チケット */
.tickets {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 24px;
}

.ticket {
  background: #fff;
  width: 300px;
  border: 2px solid #d2b48c;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 20px 26px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  transition: transform 0.5s ease;
}

.ticket:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
}

.ticket-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
  padding-bottom: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.ticket-body h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  margin: 0 0 6px 0;
  color: #2c2c2c;
}

.divider {
  border-top: 1px dashed #ccc;
  margin: 16px 0;
}

.ticket-footer {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: #777;
}

.barcode {
  width: 100%;
  height: 40px;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #333, #333 2px, transparent 2px, transparent 5px);
  margin-top: 14px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.message {
  margin-top: 40px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #5a4a42;
  line-height: 1.8;
  max-width: 600px;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 0 20px;
}

/* フェード */
.fade-in {
  animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease forwards;
  opacity: 0;
}
.fade-out {
  animation: fadeOut 0.8s ease forwards;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  to { opacity: 1; }
}
@keyframes fadeOut {
  to { opacity: 0; }
}

/* 📱 スマホ対応 */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .tickets {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .ticket {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 360px;
  }
}

function nextPage(url) {
  document.body.classList.add('fade-out');
  setTimeout(() => {
    window.location.href = url;
  }, 700);
}

window.addEventListener('pageshow', () => {
  document.body.classList.add('fade-in');
});

}
button onclick="nextPage('index.html')">トップに戻る</button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>